title: BloodCell1
---
Tami: You see anything come through here?

Blood Cell: Sure did, like a bull in a china shop. Would've done something, but I've gotta keep the beat. 

Tami: Any way you can help me catch it?

Blood Cell: Here, some of this should fire you up. 

They give Tami an ingredient, a chili pepper, which causes her taste buds to stand on edge and form to change.

Blood Cell: The booths around here are full of flavors that can help you out.


===
